PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue amending Part I (PRECIOUS METAL COINS) of the Schedule to the Royal Canadian Mint Act for the purpose of increasing the silver content of the 10¢ coin from 50% to 92.5%, and providing for the minting of a 5¢ coin having the same silver content.
